posting_body: ['Radiate Apartments', '15808 Bear Creek Parkway, Redmond, WA, 98052', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'Want more information on this unit?', 'See link (below):', '<URL>', 'SURROUND YOURSELF WITH BRILLIANCE', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath', 'Don’t just live, radiate.', 'As natural light illuminates spacious studio, one, and two bedroom floor plans, Radiate Apartment’s thoughtful design and uniquely innovative amenities unite to create a modern living experience and a warm and inviting home.', 'We offer a place for you to foster all your creative and intellectual energies in from outdoor social spaces and co-working spaces to electric car charging stations and gear storage, we have everything you could want and more.', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply)', 'Income Requirements:', '2.75x amount of rent', 'Office Hours:', 'MONDAY - TUESDAY: 10am - 6pm', 'WEDNESDAY: 11am - 6pm', 'THURSDAY-FRIDAY: 10am - 6pm', 'SATURDAY: 10am - 5pm', 'SUNDAY: CLOSED', 'Photos on this ad may not reflect all floorplans.', 'Advertised pricing and availability are subject to change without notice and cannot be guaranteed.', 'Photos on this ad may not reflect all floorplans.', 'Advertised pricing and availability are subject to change without notice and cannot be guaranteed.', 'J73zi9vLd4JG']
